<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/jan/18/">&#x27a0;</a> January 18, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="9-block-ip-identification" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.docuverse.com/blog/donpark/2007/01/18/visual-security-9-block-ip-identification">Don Park&#39;s Daily Habit - Visual Security: 9-block IP Identification</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Attractive approach to giving plausible deniability when someone fakes your name posting comments, without having your IP address posted publicly.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
